<html>
<head>
	<%- include ('./layout/head') %>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<%- include ('./layout/header_not_logged') %>
	</header>
	<main>
		<form action="/reset" class="form-signin" method="post">
			<div class="text-center pb-3">
					<p class="h1"><i class="fas fa-user"></i></p><br>
					<p class="h4">비밀번호를 찾고자하는 이메일을 입력해 주세요</p>		
			</div>

			<div class="card p-3 mt-3">
				<div class="input-group mb-2 d-flex flex-column">
					<label for="email">Email address</label>
					<input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control" required autofocus>
				</div>
				<button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Sign in</button>
			</div>
			<div class="card pt-3 mt-3 text-center">
				<p>계정이 없으시다구요? <a href='http://localhost:3000/signup'>회원가입</a>하기!</p>
			</div>

		</form>
		
	</main>




	<!-- script -->
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>
</html>